<body>

<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">
    <tr>
        <h3>촬영계획표 '{{scheduleDetail.day_title}}'</h3>
        <h5>제목부분 중앙에 오게 해주세요</h5>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>촬영계획표제목<input name="day_title" type="text" value="{{scheduleDetail.day_title}}" ></td>
